com.ericbarnhill.jvcl

Class Unroller

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ericbarnhill.jvcl.Unroller

  • public class Unroller
extends java.lang.Object
    This class generates code for unrolled convolutions. At present, this code then needs to be pasted into Unrolled.java and the code re-compiled. More streamlined approaches to adding unrolled kernels will be developed in future releases. A commented out main method which contains some scratch work in this direction has been left in the code.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    ericbarnhill
